These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, milk, tea
The people have 3 different jobs:  engineer, dressmaker, entrepreneur
House: tower, colonial, wooden
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, ritmeester, swisher
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: poppy, orchid, aconite
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, subway, train
1. the colonial house is on the right of the tower house##1
2. the wooden house is on the far left##1
3. the dressmaker is on the left of the person driving the train##1
4. the person drinking tea is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
5. the ritmeester-smoker is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
7. the engineer is between the person who growspoppy and the dressmaker##2
8. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |
| Beverage      | tea     | milk      | fanta      |
| Job          | dressmaker   | engineer   | entrepreneur       |
| House   | wooden | tower | colonial    |
| Cigar   | swisher  | fonseca    | ritmeester    |
| Flower           | orchid    | aconite    | poppy |
| Transport     | subway  | train     | bus        |

