.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-2-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, tea
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daisy, begonia, orchid
There are 3 different favourite colors: red, mauve, white
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, dutch, pakistani
City: rome, new-york, marseilles
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, bongani, tiparillo
1. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
2. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1
3. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
4. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person who likes white##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the left of the dutch##1
6. the person who growsorchid is between the pakistani and the person drinking tea##2
7. the person who likes mauve is between the person who likes white and the person traveling to marseilles##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | fanta     | cola        | tea      |
| Flower          | begonia    | orchid       | daisy  |
| Color   | white     | mauve | red    |
| Nationality   | pakistani | argentine   | dutch    |
| City           | new-york      | rome  | marseilles      |
| Cigar         | tiparillo    | bongani      | siglo |

