.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-2-3::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, swisher, fonseca
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: thriller, crime, family
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, folk, punk
There are 3 different nationalities: egyptian, french, mexican
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: soccer, biathlon, volleyball
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, december, april
1. the person watching family movies is between the mexican and the person who's sport is soccer##2
2. the french is on the left of the egyptian##1
3. the egyptian is the egyptian##1
4. the person who's sport is volleyball is the fan of folk##1
5. the french is on the left of the fan of classical##1
6. the person watching family movies is between the person watching crime movies and the siglo-smoker##2
7. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
8. the fan of folk is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
9. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |
| Cigar          | siglo  | swisher    | fonseca   |
| Movie-Genre         | thriller | family | crime |
| Music-Genre   | punk       | folk    | classical |
| Nationality   | mexican    | french  | egyptian  |
| Sport           | biathlon     | volleyball   | soccer       |
| Birthday     | december | january     | april       |

