4. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
5. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1
6. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
7. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far right##1
8. the davidoff-smoker is between the person traveling to colone and the person driving the car##2
9. the person who likes orange is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |      3       |
| Color      | lilac      | black     | orange      |
