House: craftsman, gothic-revival, wooden
There are 3 different nationalities: polish, egyptian, japanese
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, rowing, swimming
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, oliveros, tiparillo
1. the japanese is on the left of the firefighter##1
2. the tiparillo-smoker is between the ritmeester-smoker and the japanese##2
3. the bartender is on the far left##1
4. the person drinking juice is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
5. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
6. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the firefighter##1
7. the egyptian is on the right of the craftsman house##1
8. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |     3      |
| Beverage      | mirinda     | coffee   | juice      |
| Job   | bartender | firefighter  | journalist  |
| House   | craftsman       | gothic-revival  | wooden        |
| Nationality           | japanese       | egyptian   | polish |
